{
  "stem": "5883.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The little boy was four years old, and he-- they-- he knew that we were there, and-- because he used to go in the fields and sometimes pull out some carrots from the ground, some vegetables, bring it to us.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he used to say that the Germans would not live the day to kill us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "A kid, four years old-- he understood.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "While we were hiding?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nothing much, except that one incident with the car, which, you know-- oh, yes, there was another time.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was sitting and my father was reading the paper, and she noticed some people walking.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So she started-- she blew the candle out, and she started throwing the pumpkins on top of-- you know, here and there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she was talking to herself that her cow was sick and she has to find a good pumpkin.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And what happened, we heard those two people walk over to her and ask of her for directions.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then they left.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she left, and she didn't came back no more over the paper because she was afraid in case there's people watching her.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That's only two times when this happened.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She came back.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then she came-- one day she came, and she was saying that the Russians are coming in, and the Germans were leaving.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was very good to hear the news, because we knew we'd be able get out and be free.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So now, my mother waited some-- gave some time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And one day, it was [INAUDIBLE] time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my mother and father, they left us behind in the hole.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they said they will go to the city and see what's happening.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
